Invocation Name: peoria c. s. o. status
des:
Peoria CSO Status reports whether there is currently a Combined Sewer Overflow (CSO) warning from the City of Peoria for the Illinois River. 

**Disclaimer** 
No guarantee is given as to the accuracy of this information. It is recommended to verify the CSO status with the City of Peoria.

This information is provided “as is” without any representations or warranties, express or implied. No representations or warranties in relation to the information from this skill are made.
